title: Felicia's Hive 45
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bakery and restaurant offering vegan options including vegan cupcakes and cookies. Has veggie pot pies, mushroom and fennel pate, cashew cheese dip with crostini, beet-and-bean burger, ancho chili, and vegan grilled cheese.  A vegan brunch item is the brunch bowl, a layered bowl of breakfast potatoes, black beans, pan-fried tofu, squash, guacamole, and salsa.
